    <Placemark>
      <name>NAVAREA3-0034</name>
      <description>THE COORDINATOR OF COASTAL ALERTS OF UKRAINE HAS DECLARED THE FOLLOWING COASTAL APPROACH INSTRUCTIONS FOR ENTRY INTO OR EXIT FROM UKRAINIAN PORTS UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE: 1. FROM 100000 ON AUGUST 23, DAILY FROM 0200 TO 1700 UTC ROUTES TO UKRAINIAN PORTS: ROUTE No. 1.1: ROUTE FOR VESSELS WITH A DRAFT OF UP TO 8 METERS. THE WIDTH OF THE DOUBLE TRACK IS 3 NM BETWEEN THE POINTS E-H. TRACK WIDTH: 1 NM. NAVIGATION IN THE OPPOSITE DIRECTION. CENTERLINE COORDINATES OF THE ROUTE: a. 45-05.00N 030-03.00E - E</description>
      <styleUrl>#circleStyle</styleUrl>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>30.654023,46.00197,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
